M|Capi|it|[ ] Runway >12 months (healthy buffer)
M|Capi|it|[ ] Net burn decreasing over time (path to profitability)
M|Capi|it|[ ] OpEx growing slower than rv (positive operating leverage)
M|Capi|it|[ ] G&A <15% of rv (keep overhead lo)
M|Effi|it|[ ] Rule of 40 >40 (healthy balance)
M|Effi|it|[ ] Magic number >0.75 (efficient GTM)
M|Effi|it|[ ] rv growth rate > OpEx growth rate (operating leverage)
